title: Grateful Dead Live at Internationales Congress Centrum on 1990-10-20
description:
Set I
Jack Straw
Mississippi Half Step Uptown Toodleloo >
Walkin' Blues
Friend Of The Devil
Black Throated Wind
Jack A Roe
When I Paint My Masterpiece
Let It Grow >
Box Of Rain
Set II
Eyes Of The World
Samson & Delilah
Ship Of Fools
Dark Star >
Drums >
Space >
Dark Star >
Throwing Stones >
Not Fade Away

Encore:
One More Saturday Night

 
Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Vince Welnick - Keyboards
Bruce Hornsby - Piano, Accordion
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
